description:
Learn how to clean up your Gmail inbox... and keep it that way! I'll share two methods: the quick/lazy way to clean up your inbox, and the smart way where I'll show you an easy 5-step process to take control of your email inbox once and for all.

Links:
- How To Open Desktop Version of Gmail on ANY Phone (iPhone & Android): https://youtu.be/iGNRVx0fSKU

Watch this next:
- Top 15 HOT Gmail Tips & Tricks (MUST WATCH): https://youtu.be/YIXLt03BJTs

 Curious about my studio gear/equipment? Check out my budget studio spreadsheet:
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/11PLFsWyL6aau3HFUx6aQqwa9CqnO39ZWl-TeJwI7dKE
